<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="90" width="4" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="132" left="126" width="324" height="17" font="15"><b>The President</b>: I thank the Deputy Secretary-</text>
<text top="150" left="90" width="166" height="17" font="3">General for her briefing.  </text>
<text top="177" left="90" width="6" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="177" left="126" width="330" height="17" font="3">In accordance with the understanding reached in </text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="366" height="17" font="3">the Council's prior consultations, I should now like to </text>
<text top="132" left="468" width="368" height="17" font="3">invite Council members to informal consultations to </text>
<text top="150" left="468" width="263" height="17" font="3">continue our discussion on this subject.  </text>
<text top="177" left="468" width="203" height="17" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 10.50 a.m.</i> </text>
